GARY GENSLER: You're
saying it tentatively.

01:09:09.910 --> 01:09:14.297
But Tom, you're paying
Amanda 2% of your fees.

01:09:14.297 --> 01:09:16.630
Don't you want to make sure
she's validating everything?

01:09:16.630 --> 01:09:18.300
AUDIENCE: Just lost
