So a lot of miners are
not operating full nodes.

01:09:39.270 --> 01:09:41.250
They've got all
those racks of ASICs.

01:09:41.250 --> 01:09:43.560
They're running all
their electricity,

01:09:43.560 --> 01:09:46.700
and they're paying
Amanda to check on it.

01:09:46.700 --> 01:09:48.434
Don't let them down.

01:09:48.434 --> 01:09:48.934
Alene?

